    "created_at": "2017-01-16T15:45:35Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-01-16T16:31:05Z",
    "body": "Any news on this? Same issue here, Electron 1.4.7 on macOS 10.12.2. Setting the cursor to `pointer` or `none` on the container will affect only the container, but not the webview itself.\r\n\r\nEdit: I found a temporary workaround, using `webView.insertCSS()`, e.g.\r\n```js\r\nwebview.insertCSS('body { cursor: \"hidden\" !important }');\r\n```"
  },
